---
const site = {
  name: "Orken",
};
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Policies & Disclosures — {site.name}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Acceptable Use, Community Guidelines, Risk Disclaimers, and Privacy Rights for Orken Protocol" />
    <style>
      :root{
        --bg:#0b0b0d;--panel:#0f0f13;--ink:#e9ecf6;--dim:#b7bccb;--muted:#9399a7;
        --ring:#20212b;--brand:#8ab0ff;--mint:#7bffd1;--radius:18px;
        --shadow:0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.35);--glow:0 0 80px rgba(138,176,255,.12),0 0 140px rgba(123,255,209,.06);
      }
      *{box-sizing:border-box} html,body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:ui-sans-serif,system-ui,Inter,Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial}
      a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
      .container{max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px}

      /* NAV */
      .nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:40;backdrop-filter:blur(10px) saturate(1.1);background:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(11,11,13,.8),rgba(11,11,13,.35));border-bottom:1px solid var(--ring)}
      .nav-in{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:12px 0}
      .brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-weight:700}
      .sun{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(60% 60% at 50% 50%,#ff9a62 0%,#ff6b35 40%,#ff4500 100%);box-shadow:0 0 18px rgba(255,154,98,.55)}
      .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid var(--ring);background:#111115;transition:.18s;color:inherit;text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer;font:inherit}
      .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
      .btn-primary{background:linear-gradient(120deg,rgba(138,176,255,.16),rgba(123,255,209,.12));border-color:rgba(138,176,255,.35)}

      /* CONTENT */
      .content{margin:40px 0}
      .back-btn{margin-bottom:24px}
      h1{font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,36px);font-weight:800;margin:0 0 8px;color:var(--ink)}
      .effective-date{color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;margin-bottom:32px}
      h2{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 12px;color:var(--ink)}
      h3{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin:24px 0 8px;color:var(--ink)}
      p{line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 16px;color:var(--dim)}
      ul,ol{margin:0 0 16px;padding-left:24px;color:var(--dim)}
      li{margin:0 0 8px;line-height:1.6}
      .contact{margin-top:40px;padding:20px;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--ring);border-radius:var(--radius)}
      .contact h3{margin-top:0}
      .disclaimer-box{padding:20px;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--ring);border-radius:var(--radius);margin:20px 0}
      .disclaimer-box h3{color:var(--mint);margin-top:0}
      .section{margin:32px 0}
      .section h2{border-bottom:1px solid var(--ring);padding-bottom:8px}

      /* FOOTER */
      .footer{margin:80px 0 28px;border-top:1px solid var(--ring);padding-top:32px;color:var(--muted);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap}
      .footer-left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px}
      .footer-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px}
      .social-links{display:flex;gap:12px}
      .social-icon{width:20px;height:20px;opacity:0.7;transition:opacity 0.2s}
      .social-icon:hover{opacity:1}
      .footer-links{display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
      .footer-links a{color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;transition:color 0.2s}
      .footer-links a:hover{color:var(--ink)}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- NAV -->
    <div class="nav">
      <div class="container nav-in">
        <div class="brand"><span class="sun" aria-hidden="true"></span>{site.name}</div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:10px">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/marketing">← Back</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <main class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Policies & Disclosures</h1>
        <p class="effective-date">Effective date: 2025-08-01 • Contact: legal@orken.to</p>

        <div class="section">
          <h2>Acceptable Use & Community Guidelines</h2>
          
          <p>We're a discovery and community layer for the Plasma ecosystem. Our goal is to surface high-signal contributions that help builders ship better products. By using Orken, you agree not to:</p>

          <ul>
            <li><strong>Break the law or infringe rights.</strong> No illegal, hateful, harassing, doxxing, or defamatory content.</li>
            <li><strong>Spam, farm, or game the system.</strong> No sybil/bot activity, multi-account abuse, fake reviews/usage, or wash behavior.</li>
            <li><strong>Manipulate signal.</strong> Don't coordinate deceptive campaigns to distort ratings, rankings, quests, or rewards.</li>
            <li><strong>Exploit security issues outside a responsible disclosure path.</strong> No probing, brute force, or DoS.</li>
            <li><strong>Impersonate others or misrepresent your affiliation.</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Scrape at scale or circumvent technical limits;</strong> don't reverse-engineer non-open components.</li>
            <li><strong>Submit misleading feedback.</strong> Keep reviews specific, firsthand, and actionable.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Ratings & Feedback</h3>
          <p>We may weight, rank, or filter contributions for quality; we may remove content that violates these rules.</p>

          <h3>Enforcement</h3>
          <p>We can remove content, revoke points, withhold rewards, limit features, and suspend/terminate access (including wallet-level gating) for violations or risk signals. Severe/repeat abuse may be referred to relevant authorities.</p>

          <h3>Security reports</h3>
          <p>Please report vulnerabilities to <a href="mailto:security@orken.to">security@orken.to</a> with enough detail to reproduce.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <h2>Disclosure & Risk Disclaimer (Crypto / Rewards)</h2>
          
          <div class="disclaimer-box">
            <h3>⚠️ Important Notice</h3>
            <p><strong>Not financial, legal, tax, or investment advice.</strong> Do your own research.</p>
          </div>

          <h3>Platform role (like an app store)</h3>
          <p>Orken lists third-party apps, protocols, and smart contracts ("Third-Party Services") for discovery. We do not develop, operate, audit, endorse, or control them, and inclusion or ranking is not a guarantee or warranty. Interactions are directly between you and those third parties.</p>

          <h3>Smart-contract & asset risk</h3>
          <p>Smart contracts may be unaudited, exploit-prone, or fail. Digital assets can be volatile or worthless. You may lose all value. We do not custody funds or execute transactions for you, and we are not responsible for losses arising from Third-Party Services.</p>

          <h3>Quests, points, and rewards</h3>
          
          <p><strong>Promotional only.</strong> Points/badges are promotional, have no cash value, are not currency or securities, and may never convert into anything of value.</p>
          
          <p><strong>No obligation.</strong> We may modify, cap, withhold, or discontinue rewards at any time. We are not obligated to issue or convert points into tokens or any asset.</p>
          
          <p><strong>Optional participation.</strong> Quests are voluntary; you decide whether to complete them.</p>
          
          <p><strong>Eligibility & fraud controls.</strong> We may require verification (including KYC/AML for certain payouts), apply geographic/sanctions restrictions, and disqualify or claw back rewards for abuse (e.g., sybil/bots/falsified activity).</p>
          
          <p><strong>Taxes.</strong> You are solely responsible for any taxes related to rewards or activity.</p>

          <h3>No advice</h3>
          <p>Content on Orken (including listings, ratings, comments, and summaries) is for community/information purposes only and not investment, legal, tax, or financial advice. See our <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a> and <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for more.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <h2>Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information (CPRA)</h2>
          
          <p>If you are a California resident, you may opt out of the "sale" or "sharing" of personal information as defined by the California Privacy Rights Act (CPRA).</p>

          <h3>How to opt out</h3>
          
          <p><strong>Submit a request:</strong> Use our CPRA form here: <a href="/do-not-sell">/do-not-sell</a> (or email <a href="mailto:privacy@orken.to">privacy@orken.to</a> with the subject "CPRA Opt-Out").</p>
          
          <p><strong>Cookie-based sharing:</strong> Manage analytics/advertising cookies in <a href="/cookies">Cookie Preferences</a> (also accessible from our Cookies page).</p>
          
          <p><strong>Authorized agents:</strong> You may use an authorized agent; we may require proof of authorization and identity verification.</p>

          <h3>Your other privacy rights</h3>
          <p>Depending on your region, you may have rights to access, delete, correct, or restrict processing of your data, and to withdraw consent where applicable. See our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for details, or contact <a href="mailto:privacy@orken.to">privacy@orken.to</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact">
          <h3>Contact</h3>
          <p>For questions about these policies, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:legal@orken.to">legal@orken.to</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- FOOTER -->
      <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-left">
          <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} {site.name}. Built for the Orken ecosystem.</span>
        </div>
